  <summary date="2017-11-09T05:00:00Z" status="Introduced in House">Current Employee Representation Act

This bill amends the National Labor Relations Act to allow an employee or group of employees to petition for a union certification election: (1) if fewer than 50% of the current bargaining unit were unit members in the last certification election, or (2) no certification election was conducted for such unit.</summary>
